query:
SELECT sv.id, v.name, sv.score, sv.definition 
FROM selected_values sv
JOIN values v ON sv.value_id = v.id
WHERE sv.session_id = '0wMRam3E11CfNoQ5AQKyP'
ORDER BY sv.score DESC
LIMIT 15;
